# Data Communication and Computer Networks (DCN)

This folder contains the laboratory programs, experiments, and practical assignments completed as part of the Data Communication and Computer Networks (DCN) course.

## Contents

- Network Topologies
- IP Addressing and Subnetting
- Routing Protocols
- Switching Concepts
- Socket Programming
- Client-Server Communication
- Network Simulation
- Packet Analysis
- Lab Assignments

## Technologies Used

- Cisco Packet Tracer
- Wireshark
- C / Java (Socket Programming)

## Objective

To understand the fundamentals of computer networks through practical implementation, network simulation, protocol analysis, and communication between networked systems.
